high_descs: Turn around, walk forward, turn right near the fridge, walk straight and turn left to face the stove.
Pick up the pan from on top of the stove.
Turn around, walk to the right to go back to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the pan in it, close the fridge, let it cool for a while, open the fridge, pick it up again and close the fridge.
Go to the right and turn left to face the dishwasher.
Put the pan on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold pan on the counter top on top of the dishwasher.

high_descs: Walk around the kitchen counter to the stove on your left.
Grab a pan from the stove.
Walk to the front of the fridge on your left.
Place the pan in the fridge, then grab it.
Walk to the kitchen counter between the fridge and stove.
Place the pan on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Chill a pan and put it on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around to your left walk straight then turn right head to the  stove on your left
Pick up the pan on the  stove
Turn left then walk straight head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in the pan then take it out and close the fridge
Turn right walk straight face the counter beside the toaster
Put the pan on the counter beside the toaster
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled pan on the counter
